headline: 10 Stock Splits Investors Could See Happen by 2026
summary: There have been a few high-profile stock splits this year, most recently O'Reilly Automotive.  A number of stocks now have share prices over $1,000.  If the bull market continues, we're likely to see some more stock splits.
